Package: vindecoder
Type: Package
Title: VIN Decoding Using VPIC Lite Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "weihuang.wong@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to decode Vehicle Identification Numbers (VINs) 
    using a lightweight implementation of the VPIC (Vehicle Product Information 
    Catalog) database. The package includes functions to initialize an in-memory 
    database from CSV files and decode VINs to extract vehicle information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    DBI,
    duckdb,
    tools
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
